      <section eId="sec_31_8_6">
        <num>31-8-6</num>
        <content>
          <p>Upon certification approved by the department, any participating county may receive credit for direct expenditures made during the period covered by the budget by the county to a hospital or hospitals when such expenditures can be shown to have been made for the care of indigent residents as defined in this Code section.</p>
